        • public static String substringAfterLast(String string, String separator)

          Returns the substring of a string that follows the last occurence of a separator.

          Largely replicated and slightly updated from the apache.commons.lang.StringUtils method of the same name.

          Parameters:
          string - the String to get a substring from, may not be null
          separator - the String to search for, may not be null
          Returns:
          the substring after the last occurrence of the separator or an empty string if not found.
